{"tid":1056582,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有冇睇過Tvb套缺宅男女","createTime":"2019-03-11T09:59:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-14T04:59:44.000Z","uid":227650,"like":15,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9bd74de4386a9461a07fca1933f501d303ebe2c2","tid":1056582,"uid":227650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T09:59:10.000Z","msg":"當年有人話呢套戲係抄蝸居，係咪抄就唔知啦，不過我覺得有樣做得好嘅地方就係啲主要角色迫埋喺同一間屋度;呢樣嘢夠曬貼地。<br />\n<br />\n苗僑偉唔再做警察角色;做平民、好想買樓嘅裝修佬， 謝天華做返類似賤man嘅角色，吳卓羲唔係做衝動警察角色，仲有做巴渣潑辣大肚婆嘅黃智雯入型入格、搶曬焦點。<br />\n<br />\n呢段苗僑偉屌鳩謝天華嘅片段，當年都好多人讚;不過有高登仔話如果呢段戲唔係苗僑偉做，由第二個做效果可能會更好 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/qP68F1gGIRI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqP68F1gGIRI&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FG58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=35df5791\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qP68F1gGIRI</a><br />\n<br />\n呢套戲正在反映到香港樓價嘅問題，主角一生人就係為層樓奔波一生。"},{"pid":"8b73a8a1f218ccc4482e0354cdafe8cbe2a88727","tid":1056582,"uid":227650,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T10:01:03.000Z","msg":"仲有首主題曲都好好聽，吳卓羲同鍾嘉欣合唱 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/I9gHR1KP0hI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FI9gHR1KP0hI&d=JC%2BoF4fRaZyKvWcl7nla%2FG58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=60d696d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/I9gHR1KP0hI</a>"},{"pid":"6dcd834606d5e12cbe50ed8e125d8813fb3fa2e3","tid":1056582,"uid":151926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T10:02:37.000Z","msg":"前兩年先重播過"},{"pid":"17eb5208f6b29f1ce0937ffb8d393d46e1d2b209","tid":1056582,"uid":49197,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T10:07:53.000Z","msg":"麻麻地,感情戲同家庭戲仲多過講樓既問題"},{"pid":"78bc25bd6f9800e93c664d5767e2b524a4073b72","tid":1056582,"uid":227650,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"17eb5208f6b29f1ce0937ffb8d393d46e1d2b209","tid":1056582,"uid":49197,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-11T10:07:53.000Z","msg":"麻麻地,感情戲同家庭戲仲多過講